{"tid":1534123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北非諜影Casablanca教你比噓國歌更有效既建構民族認同方法","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T18:38:22.000Z","uid":161781,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"761cc55de6d45e933ff42c0018414e6cf44481aa","tid":1534123,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HM-E2H1ChJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHM-E2H1ChJM&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=2f0b1222\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HM-E2H1ChJM</a><br />\n<br />\n見到有post話睇波時噓國歌<br />\n但其實有方法比只噓國歌更好<br />\n<br />\nCasablanca中德國少校係酒館唱起德國軍歌《守衛萊茵》，主角睇唔過眼，帶領一眾酒館內既法國人<br />\n合唱法國國歌《馬賽曲》，最後蓋過德國軍官既歌聲<br />\n<br />\n值得一提既係，戲中合唱馬賽曲既有真實法國人，原本劇本並無安排佢地需要流淚，但可以睇到幾個合唱既演員都情不自禁咁流淚（時值1942）<br />\n<br />\n大家如果睇波，唔一定要噓國歌，可以大合唱一首代表到香港既歌，更能激勵人心<br />\n<br />\n最後附上馬賽曲首節歌詞，俄國二月革命亦曾將其定為國歌，歌詞同現今香港情況暗合<br />\n<br />\nAllons enfants de la Patrie,<br />\n一起走吧，祖國的子民們<br />\nLe jour de gloire est arriv&eacute;！<br />\n榮耀之日來臨了<br />\nContre nous de la tyrannie,<br />\n那暴政對著我們<br />\nL&rsquo;&eacute;tendard sanglant est lev&eacute;！<br />\n升起了染血的軍旗<br />\nEntendez-vous dans les campagnes<br />\n你們可聽到在鄉間<br />\nMugir ces f&eacute;roces soldats&nbsp;?<br />\n殘暴士兵們的吼叫<br />\nIls viennent jusque dans vos bras<br />\n他們會來到你們跟前<br />\nEgorger vos fils,vos compagnes&nbsp;！<br />\n殘殺你們的孩子，你們的伴侶<br />\nAux armes, citoyens!<br />\n拿起武器，公民們，<br />\nFormez vos bataillons!<br />\n排好你們的隊伍！<br />\nMarchons, marchons&nbsp;!<br />\n進軍，進軍！<br />\nQu'un sang impur<br />\n讓不潔之血<br />\nAbreuve nos sillons&nbsp;!<br />\n灌溉我們的壕溝！"},{"pid":"ac7fa66d9de4b49ffc9051abc12f046466209306","tid":1534123,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"唱美國國歌"},{"pid":"637f5af38ca1412852e00d24e965a84c5f260393","tid":1534123,"uid":210190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"鬼識唱法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唱美國國歌都好過佢"},{"pid":"e89c965bac1e80bbe1f37e519b197cc8e90603b7","tid":1534123,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"637f5af38ca1412852e00d24e965a84c5f260393","tid":1534123,"uid":210190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"鬼識唱法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唱美國國歌都好過佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"唔識睇中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b93cea30daa990311863c13a048c7f229e5484","tid":1534123,"uid":197958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6252e68dca8d8097d191aa0be7e403522e4bc9a4","tid":1534123,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:36:58.000Z","msg":"呢個post值得推返上嚟"},{"pid":"ee94c006fa396818280ab4bcd88fa50e4e851508","tid":1534123,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:38:22.000Z","msg":"你有現場睇過波 就知無可能啦"}]}